    <p>Workhub's founder discovered a strong link between safety compliance and recognition early on in Workhub's (formerly SafetySync) life. This concept become Rewards (<a href="https://www.workhub.com/features/branded-apparel/" target="_blank">read more about Workhub Rewards here</a>). Collecting points, spending them on Rewards, and have them shipped directly from us (customization of all soft good available in small batches) has proved incredibly appealing to beleaguered safety admins.</p>
    <p class="mt-4"><strong>The Bet</strong><br />The high adoption and enjoyment of Workhub Rewards by workers isn't <em>because</em> of the catalog... it's in <em>spite</em> of it. For quick and easy organizational adoption, the catalog has to more closely follow Ecommerce norms.</p>
