  <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2 col-md-8 mb-4 mb-md-0" style="position: relative; z-index: 1;">
    <div class="case-study-info">
      <h5 class="mb-2">That unfortunately doesn't look (or work!) great</h5>
      <p>Rewards was especially hard hit when SafetySync became workhub. Something was lost in translation and an opportunity to bring Rewards into the modern era of Ecommerce patterns and flows was missed. No meaningful change in conversions was made in years.</p> 
      <p>No matter how many points you give a worker (and mind that they’re worth 25 cents each!) they always make about one redemption on the outside of a year (12.5 months to be exact). This has ballooned potential points in the system that have yet to be converted into revenue for us. I strongly believed that updating the catalog could help with this and as product owner of this segment I was ready to take the plunge.</p>
      <p>Objectives:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Standardize the wildly non-standard design</li>
        <li>Integrate more modern common flows</li>
        <li>Make everything flashier (we want users to convert)</li>
        <li>Give more reasons to redeem now</li>
        <li>Add lazy loading to get the user to the products faster</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

